.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, september, october, may, july
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, helicopter, quad-bike, jet-ski
There 5 different types of food: cabbage, nectarine, kiwi, peach, banana
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: aprilmaster, disaster, action, spy, zombie
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, skydiving, rock-climbing, photography, sudoku
1. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's birthday is in october
2. the person driving the swedish is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing
3. the person driving the subway is the person eating peach
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may
5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person eating nectarine
6. the person watching action movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving
7. the person who's birthday is in july is the person watching disaster movies
8. the person eating kiwi is in the middle
9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left
10. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking
11. the person who's hobby is sudokus is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies
12. the person watching aprilmaster movies is the person eating cabbage
13. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching spy movies
14. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april
15. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person eating banana

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Birthday		|    july	|     april	|      october	|     september	|     may	|
| Transport	|   quad-bike	|    subway	|    snowmobile	|    helicopter	|    swedish	|
| Hobby		|     hiking	|    sudoku	|     skydiving	|     photography	|      rock-climbing	|
| Food	|    banana	|     peach	|     kiwi	|    nectarine	|      cabbage	|
| Movie-Genre		|   disaster	|    zombie	|  action	|    spy	|   aprilmaster	|
